# Portfolio Harness (Agentic OS)

This project uses the shared portfolio harness from `hotproductsdot-v2/agentic-os`.

## Delegation model

- **You (Cursor):** implement and review code in this repo
- **Hermes:** orchestrate cron, cross-project research, morning briefs — not primary coder
- **Oracle:** synthesis across Cursor sessions, Claude Code, and Obsidian

## Non-negotiables

- Secrets in repo-root `.env` only — never commit
- No force-push to main; confirm destructive git/deploy operations
- Use `--dry-run` for publish/deploy automation unless user explicitly approves
- Minimize diff scope — match existing conventions in this repo

